1
00:00:09,119 --> 00:00:10,000
Qibao

2
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:13,160
Your loving boyfriend

3
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:15,720
Got you your favorite milk tea!

4
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:16,600
Come on, tell me,

5
00:00:16,839 --> 00:00:18,199
do you love your boyfriend more,

6
00:00:18,199 --> 00:00:19,960
or the milk tea more?

7
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:21,600
Who's there?

8
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:25,399
Happy birthday to you

9
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:29,079
Happy birthday to you

10
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:32,759
Happy birthday to you

11
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:36,640
Happy birthday to you

12
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:38,880
Tianfang, happy birthday.

13
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:40,799
Thank you.

14
00:00:41,159 --> 00:00:42,240
You're the first girl in my life

15
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,439
to ever celebrate my birthday.

16
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,600
I'm yours for life.

17
00:00:47,719 --> 00:00:48,200
Come on,

18
00:00:48,799 --> 00:00:49,520
make a wish.

19
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:51,960
I...

20
00:00:53,039 --> 00:00:55,200
I'm so happy and so overwhelmed right now,

21
00:00:55,399 --> 00:00:56,960
I don't know what to wish for.

22
00:00:57,479 --> 00:00:58,479
I just want

23
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,759
to be with you for the rest of my life.

24
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,039
Then how about

25
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:05,840
we get married?

26
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:10,400
Did I scare you?

27
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:13,760
Just pretend I was joking.

28
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,159
No, it's not that.

29
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,040
I never know

30
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,599
if tomorrow

31
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:20,959
or the unexpected will come first.

32
00:01:21,319 --> 00:01:22,640
I don't want to live with regrets.

33
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,319
Qibao,

34
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:37,519
will you marry me?

35
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,040
I will.

36
00:02:13,479 --> 00:02:14,120
So beautiful.

37
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,360
Today went pretty well.

38
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:26,199
Ma'am.

39
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:26,919
Fox.

40
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,879
I'm here.

41
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,800
No, old man.

42
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,639
I have a name. It's He Siqi.

43
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,560
You're Fox.

44
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:34,159
Old man.

45
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:35,039
Whatever, whatever.

46
00:02:35,159 --> 00:02:35,840
Fox, listen.

47
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:38,360
I raised a Speckled Hen.

48
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,199
Raised her for three years.

49
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:42,919
She laid two eggs every day.

50
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:44,000
And those eggs,

51
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,759
their nutritional value

52
00:02:45,759 --> 00:02:47,919
was rich and varied.

53
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:49,599
That's the first I've ever heard

54
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:51,560
of a hen laying two eggs a day.

55
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:53,000
Of course there are.

56
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:56,280
She's the only one of her kind in the world.

57
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:59,080
A fighter among hens.

58
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:01,360
In the morning I fed her corn,

59
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:04,000
in the afternoon I fed her grain,

60
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,039
in the evening I fed her millet.

61
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,319
Three hundred and sixty days a year,

62
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:10,719
I waited on her in every way.

63
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:12,039
In our whole village,

64
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:12,879
everyone knew

65
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:15,039
I had this amazing hen.

66
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:21,159
But a Weasel snatched her away!

67
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,759
A Weasel?

68
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,639
Why are you crying again?

69
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,759
It was him.

70
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,520
It was him.

71
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,159
It was him!

72
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,400
Oh my!

73
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,560
My dear old man.

74
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,759
Are you serious?

75
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,000
You just watch.

76
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:43,759
I won't let you down.

77
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:44,639
Here, take this.

78
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,639
So this Weasel you mentioned,

79
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,479
where is he now?

80
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,280
He's hiding

81
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,919
in that abandoned building in Ludong Village.

82
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,319
Um,

83
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,560
I'll call Chu Feng.

84
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,159
Okay.

85
00:03:58,919 --> 00:03:59,520
Call him right now.

86
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:00,719
Fox.

87
00:04:01,479 --> 00:04:02,360
It's for you.

88
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,039
Hurry.

89
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,199
It's all Yu Tianfang's fault we're in this mess.

90
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,360
We'll get our revenge sooner or later.

91
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:16,600
That chicken soup smells amazing.

92
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,360
It must be ready.

93
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,759
Good food's worth the wait.

94
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,680
Um, Boss Hui,

95
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,519
this Speckled Hen will get tough if we cook it too long.

96
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:32,800
You, you, you...

97
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,160
Look how beautiful this chicken fat is.

98
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,879
Cook it longer, it'll be tender.

99
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:36,959
Wait a bit more.

100
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,160
Trouble's coming.

101
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,240
Boss Hui.

102
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:44,399
You go first, I'll cover you.

103
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:45,560
Forget covering!

104
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:46,480
Split up!

105
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,040
Move!

106
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,680
Whether or not I escape today,

107
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:51,240
I'm going to kill Yu Tianfang.

108
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,240
It's still warm.

109
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,040
They can't have gotten far.

110
00:05:07,319 --> 00:05:07,920
After them!

111
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,279
This bed...

112
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,600
it won't collapse, will it?

113
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,920
Definitely not.

114
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:17,720
Look.

115
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,160
Be gentle.

116
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,439
Then... like this?

117
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,360
You can't be so rough.

118
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,600
You need to be gentler.

119
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:29,319
Gentle.

120
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:30,959
Is this okay?

121
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:36,399
I'm still a little worried.

122
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,199
Don't worry.

123
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:39,639
This bed is really sturdy.

124
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,519
I was thinking,

125
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:43,160
once I earn a bit more money,

126
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:45,240
I'll get a new one, super big,

127
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,360
with a super soft mattress.

128
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,079
It doesn't matter what the bed is like.

129
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,120
What matters

130
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:53,480
is the person.

131
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:34,199
The bed collapsed!

132
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,120
Don't be afraid,

133
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:52,680
Qibao.

134
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,399
I'll go check outside.

135
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:56,319
If you sense anything is wrong,

136
00:06:56,319 --> 00:06:57,600
call Chu Feng right away.

137
00:06:59,079 --> 00:06:59,959
Be careful.

138
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:12,480
I'll be fine.

139
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,000
You bastard.

140
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,399
You're finally here.

141
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:16,839
This blade is the Heavenly Sword,

142
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:19,040
descendant of the Dragon Slayer.

143
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,079
Are you scared yet?

144
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,240
Spare me!

145
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:36,080
Just a little spooky atmosphere

146
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,759
and you're scared half to death.

147
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,759
Pfft!

148
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,279
What a crap killer.

149
00:08:40,279 --> 00:08:41,759
Worse than me, a pork butcher.

150
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:44,919
Chu Feng.

151
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,480
Look who I caught.

152
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,360
My moves were absolutely badass.

153
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,600
But let me be clear,

154
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:53,759
this is self-defense.

155
00:08:53,759 --> 00:08:55,519
Ma Xiaojun broke into my house to kill me.

156
00:08:55,519 --> 00:08:56,519
Whether he lives or dies

157
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:57,879
has nothing to do with me.

158
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:58,879
Where is he?

159
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:10,840
I surrender, I surrender, I surrender!

160
00:09:11,799 --> 00:09:12,600
I...

161
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,159
Boss Hui!

162
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:15,679
Run!

163
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:20,919
No, wait.

164
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,799
He was just lying right here.

165
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:24,320
I swear I'm not lying.

166
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,519
I just beat him half to death.

167
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,600
He was lying right here.

168
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,240
I'll go chase him down now.

169
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,559
This one,

170
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,639
leave him to me.

171
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,759
Even heroes need to know the law.

172
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,799
Go back and stay with He Siqi.

173
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,039
First thing tomorrow morning,

174
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,360
the two of you come together

175
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,399
to give me your statements.

176
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:40,960
And

177
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,799
stay safe.

178
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:44,720
Got it.

179
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:49,320
I'm off.

180
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:07,960
How did I let him get away?

181
00:10:08,279 --> 00:10:09,120
You're back.

182
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,120
Let me take a look.

183
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:11,960
Are you hurt?

184
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,639
I was channeling divine kung fu,

185
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,279
and that bastard

186
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:17,279
couldn't lay a finger on me.

187
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:18,360
Don't worry, Qibao.

188
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:19,440
Oh, right.

189
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:20,799
I just remembered.

190
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,000
It's getting late.

191
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:25,279
I should head out to restock.

192
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,480
Lately,

193
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,000
our pork stall has been doing pretty well.

194
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,360
I was thinking,

195
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:30,960
once I save up a bit more,

196
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:33,320
we can rent a nicer place.

197
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,720
I can't keep

198
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,080
letting you live a hard life with me.

199
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:38,840
As long as I'm with you,

200
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,279
I'm happy.

201
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:41,399
It's not hard at all.

202
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:43,720
Really.

203
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:45,799
Look.

204
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:48,120
Just now,

205
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,960
there was deafening thunder.

206
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,120
And now,

207
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:53,240
the sky is full of stars.

208
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,320
Look,

209
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,519
how beautiful.

210
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:58,159
Yeah.

211
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,480
Look.

212
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,039
I see them.

213
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:09,559
Let's go.

214
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,000
Talk and laugh.

215
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,080
Be natural.

216
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:14,240
Okay.

217
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:16,759
Groom, move a little closer to the bride.

218
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:19,159
Don't be nervous.

219
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,399
Smile at each other.

220
00:11:21,559 --> 00:11:22,720
Good.

221
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:24,000
Good.

222
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:35,320
Okay.

223
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:37,919
What's wrong?

224
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,360
Nothing.

225
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:43,120
Groom, move a little closer to the bride.

226
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,399
Tianfang.

227
00:11:47,399 --> 00:11:47,879
Tianfang.

228
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,080
This is what you get for betraying me.

229
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:54,519
I'll make you lose the ones you love most.

230
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,399
First, your mother.

231
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:58,519
Then, your fiancé.

232
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,559
What's wrong?

233
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,399
Did you have a nightmare?

234
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,600
I'm fine.

235
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,960
It's probably because

236
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,600
the shoot today was exhausting.

237
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,320
You'd barely gotten in the car

238
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,120
before you fell asleep.

239
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,399
It's okay.

240
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,000
Good thing we shot it quickly.

241
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:19,000
It looks like it's about to rain.

242
00:12:21,799 --> 00:12:22,840
My dear wife,

243
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:25,559
what do you feel like eating later?

244
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:27,399
Some barbecue?

245
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:28,960
Hot pot?

246
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,360
Pickled fish?

247
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:33,279
Or your handsome, charming,

248
00:12:33,279 --> 00:12:35,159
adorable husband?

249
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,960
Hey, keep your voice down!

250
00:12:38,159 --> 00:12:39,000
Have you no shame?

251
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:39,799
No way.

252
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,799
I'm just not the kind of guy

253
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:43,600
who hides his love deep inside.

254
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,519
You know how I am.

255
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:46,000
I-I-I just love to show off.

256
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,559
I finally managed

257
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:49,360
to marry such a beautiful wife.

258
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,759
Of course I want to proudly

259
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:52,279
let the whole world know!

260
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:55,200
Baby, I love you.

261
00:12:56,159 --> 00:12:57,480
Okay, okay.

262
00:12:58,279 --> 00:12:59,120
I love you too.

263
00:13:00,679 --> 00:13:02,080
Then give me a kiss.

264
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:12,919
Qibao!

265
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:24,799
Qibao!

266
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:26,480
Tianfang!

267
00:13:26,799 --> 00:13:27,720
Go to hell!

268
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,279
Tianfang!

269
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,440
Siqi, don't come down!

270
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,000
Qibao!

271
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:50,600
Qibao!

272
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,320
Hey!

273
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,200
Tianfang.

274
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,679
I'll give you a choice.

275
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,919
She dies, or you die?

276
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:11,080
Kill me, torture me,

277
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,240
do it to me.

278
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,840
We'll settle all our scores,

279
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,120
old and new, together.

280
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,879
Truly worthy of being Chen Hui's woman.

281
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,080
You've got guts.

282
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,519
Qibao!

283
00:14:23,799 --> 00:14:24,480
Qibao!

284
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:25,480
Qibao!

285
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:28,759
Qibao!
